title: Jumping Jacks
details: Jumping Jacks are a cardio exercise that can help to increase heart rate, improve endurance and strengthen muscles.

title: Wall Push-ups
details: Wall Push-ups are a strength exercise that can help to tone the chest, shoulders, and triceps muscles.

title: Plank
details: Plank is a strength exercise that can help to tone the core muscles.

title: High Knees
details: High Knees are a cardio exercise that can help to increase heart rate, improve endurance and strengthen leg muscles.

title: Squats
details: Squats are a strength exercise that can help to tone the lower body muscles.

title: Lunges
details: Lunges are a strength exercise that can help to tone the lower body muscles.

title: Calf Raises
details: Calf Raises are a strength exercise that can help to tone the calf muscles.

title: Bicycle Crunches
details: Bicycle Crunches are a strength exercise that can help to tone the core muscles.

title: Arm Circles
details: Arm Circles are a strength exercise that can help to tone the shoulder muscles.

title: Mountain climbers
details: Mountain climbers are a dynamic exercise that works your core, legs, and arms. It's a great cardiovascular workout and can help improve coordination and balance.

title: Side lunges
details: Side lunges are an excellent exercise for strengthening the legs and improving flexibility. They target the muscles in the inner and outer thighs and help improve balance and stability.

title: Desk Push-Ups
details: Desk push-ups are a quick and easy way to get your heart rate up and strengthen your arms, chest, and core.
